list.name: Dos Si Dos
list.description: Everything you need to elevate your adventure. Our Ready to Roll resealable pouches include high-quality, pre-ground flower, unbleached hemp rolling papers, and crutches.

list.name: Ray Charles
list.description:
One of the most classic Grassroots strains, Ray Charles is a favorite for Indica lovers. With

d e e p greens highlighted by orange stigma, it's not hard to spot Ray in a lineup. When it

comes to aroma, the Myrcene makes its presence known quickly, with a sweet mango scent to it.

Dig a little deeper and you'll find a fuel aroma that carries over into the flavor. On the exhale,

a minty taste sticks around on your palate. With the realxing mental and physical effects, this

strain is a reported favorite for sleep and pain management.

list.name: Gush Mints x Runtz
list.description: Gush Mints x Runtz is well-balanced, offering a combination of uplifting and euphoric feelings, along with a deep sense of relaxation. Its dominant terpenes Limonene, Linalool, and Caryophyllene and may help to elevate mood and relieve stress without causing sedation which makes it a great choice for social situations or for unwinding after a long day. Packaging may vary by state. Maryland packaging shown.

list.name: Animal Face
list.description: Animal Face is a soulful strain from venerable Seed Junky Genetics. This indica dominant strain is the perfect mix of pedigree, palate and power. A love child of the classic Face Off OG and Animal Mints, its frosty buds and bright orange hairs produce a unique citrusy, sugary, nutty flavor with hints of earth and pine. Best reserved for after-hours, this special cut will melt cares and stress away.

list.name: Berry Payton
list.description: Cross of Gary Payton x Tropical Runtz from Tiki Madman, offering a vibrant, fruity palate with creamy, candy-like undertones from its Gary Payton lineage. This smooth, flavorful hybrid is known for its upbeat, creative effects, balanced by the grounding presence of terpenes like linalool and caryophyllene.

list.name: Pineapple Skunk
list.description: Seed & Strain is deeply rooted in the land, with every product hand-harvested to ensure quality and care. Our dedication to craftsmanship reflects the hardworking spirit of the community we serve. Our Pineapple Skunk delivers big, beautiful hugs every time that carry earthy, lemony, hoppy, pine aromas. Expect big Indica feels, great for unwinding from a stressful day, relaxing the body and mind.

list.name: LA Kush Cake
list.description:
Grown by SunMed, Belushi’s Farm genetics are hand harvested and cured by a small and passionate cultivation team to deliver high-testing, complex cultivars.

SunMed grows Belushi's Farm's premium cultivars in full-spectrum sunlight to produce potent, flavorful and aromatic buds.

______________________________________________________________________________________

Belushi's Farm is both a place and a mission. Spread across 93 acres on the Rogue River in Southern Oregon, the farm welcomes friends from near and far for music, celebration and wellness and is home to the Belushi's Farm family of cannabis brands. By sharing the land and its offerings, performer and long-time proponent of cannabis, Jim Belushi, has created a gateway for connection and joy where the sun, water and air make the perfect combination to sustain naturally powerful and beautiful cannabis plants.                                  

SunMed Growers and Belushi's Farm share a commitment to sustainable cultivation, social responsibility and the beneficial properties of the cannabis plant. SunMed cultivates Belushi's Farm's house strains in full-spectrum sunlight to produce potent, flavorful and aromatic buds.
